val at Richfield Avenue. CREDIT: C Brandon/Redferns/Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> Speaking about Bring Me The Horizon moving to the top of the bill for 2025, following them being <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/bring-me-the-horizon-reading-festival-2022-review-setlist-photos-3299213">co-headliners with Arctic Monkeys in 2022</a> , Benn said: “Bring Me are one of the most amazing bands to work with.</p><p> “I&#39;ve no idea of their economics, but it always seems that no matter how much money we pay them, they&#39;re determined to spend more on giving the fans what they want in terms of production and visuals.”</p><p> He continued: “That for me, is just an incredible statement from a band to just want to please their fans. <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/bring-me-the-horizon-reading-festival-2022-review-setlist-photos-3299213">他们上次在2022年打球</a>绝对是非凡的。 They&#39;re definitely going to top it.”</p><p> The huge 2024 instalment saw <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/liam-gallagher-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-oasis-reunion-noel-3787153">Liam Gallagher</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/lana-del-rey-reading-2024-live-review-setlist-photos-3786852">Lana Del Rey</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/fred-again-reading-festival-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786905">Fred Again..</a> , <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/blink-182-reading-2024-review-photo-setlist-3786510">Blink-182,</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/catfish-the-bottlemen-reading-festival-2024-review-setlist-photos-3787168">Catfish &amp; The Bottlemen</a> and <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/gerry-cinnamon-live-at-reading-2024-review-photos-setlist-3786511">Gerry Cinnamon</a> top the bill. You can find a list of <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/reading-leeds-festival-2024-review-best-bits-liam-gallagher-lana-del-rey-fontaines-dc-3787423">NME&#39;s top moments from that edition here</a> .</p><p> The post <a 