这些是2024年最受欢迎的Netflix电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-were-the-most-viewed-netflix-movies-in-2024-3841993?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=these-were-the-most-viewed-netflix-movies-in-2024Victoria Luxford Thu, 27 Feb 2025 16:49:19 +0000 Film NewsNewsOscars https://www.nme.com/?p=3841993 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> A Taron Egerton thriller is top of the list, while Emilia Pérez misses out</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-were-the-most-viewed-netflix-movies-in-2024-3841993">These were the most viewed Netflix movies in 2024</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Netflix" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Netflix-picture-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taron-egerton">Taron Egerton</a> thriller <em>Carry-On</em> was <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix&#39;s</a> most watched movie in the second half of 2024, according to statistic provided by the streaming service in a new report.</p><ul><li> <strong>READ MORE:</strong> <a href="https://www.nme.com/lists/end-of-year/best-films-2024-3817632">The 20 best films of 2024</a></li></ul><p> The twice-yearly engagement report, titled <em>What We Watched</em> , calculates views by dividing total hours viewed by runtime. <em>Carry-On</em> , a <em>Die Hard</em> -style thriller set in an airport, drew over 137Million views, topping the list of most watched films.</p><p> Action dominated the top four, with <em>The Union</em> starring <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/halle-berry">Halle Berry</a> and Mark Wahlberg coming second with 131Million, <em>Rebel Ridge</em> third with 129Million, and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/eddie-murphy">Eddie Murphy</a> sequel <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/beverly-hills-cop-axel-f"><em>Beverly Hill Cop: Axel F</em></a> fourth with just over 97Million.</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lindsay-lohan">Lindsay Lohan</a> comedy <em>Our Little Secret</em> was fifth with 81Million, family musical <em>Sing: Thriller</em> sixth with 77Million, and <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nicole-kidman">Nicole Kidman</a> /Zac Efron romantic comedy <em>A Family Affair</em> was seventh with 74Million.</p><p> Rounding our the top ten was sci-fi drama <em>Uglies</em> (72Million), Sam Raimi produced thriller <em>Don&#39;t Move</em> (69Million), and Christmas classic <em>Dr Zeuss&#39; The Grinch</em> (66Million). </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Carry-On |官方预告片| Netflix" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/KS0XacjMmOc?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Surprisingly, <em>Emilia Pérez,</em> which earned 13 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/oscars">Oscar</a> nominations including Best Picture, was nowhere near the top ten. While it was released in November on the streaming service, it finished 1,778th out of 8,686 features viewed from July to December. <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/angelina-jolie">Angelina Jolie&#39;s</a> biopic <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/maria"><em>Maria</em></a> also faired poorly, drawing just 800,000 views.</p><p> The report boasted a 5 per cent increase of viewing time for Netflix, totalling over 94Billion hours watched across all programming. The company has big titles planned for 2025, sequel <em>Wake Up Dead Man: A Knives Out Mystery</em> starring <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/daniel-craig">Daniel Craig</a> set for the second half of the year, while <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/guillermo-del-toro">Guillermo Del Toro&#39;s</a> adaptation of <em>Frankenstein</em> is slated for November.</p><p> <em>Carry-On</em> was directed by Jaume Collet-Serra ( <em>Black Adam</em> ) and stars Egerton as Ethan Kopek, a young airport security officer who is blackmailed into letting a nerve agent onboard a flight during Christmas Eve.</p><p> There has been no word on a sequel, but <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/is-carry-on-2-going-to-be-made-3823028">many fans have speculated that it could be a real possibility given the nature of the premise</a> .</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/these-were-the-most-viewed-netflix-movies-in-2024-3841993">These were the most viewed Netflix movies in 2024</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
